### Login to get token
POST http://localhost/api/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "password"
}

### Set token variable (replace with actual token from login response)
@token = YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

###

### List all equipement appartements
GET http://localhost/api/equipement-appartement
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Create a new equipement appartement
POST http://localhost/api/equipement-appartement
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "appartement_id": 1,
  "nom_equipement": "Lit",
  "quantite": 2,
  "etat": "Neuf"
}

###

### Show a specific equipement appartement
GET http://localhost/api/equipement-appartement/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Update an equipement appartement
PUT http://localhost/api/equipement-appartement/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nom_equipement": "Lit double",
  "quantite": 1,
  "etat": "Bon"
}

###

### Delete an equipement appartement
DELETE http://localhost/api/equipement-appartement/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
